logger = get_context_logger(__name__)

pipeline_info_helper.py
Lines 774-780
                    logger.warning(
                        f"✓ Updated pipeline info using discovered key: {client_id}/{discovered_key}. "
                        f"ACTION REQUIRED: Migrate record to normalized format '{brand_retailer_key}'. "
